    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>You are invited to a friend's birthday. You respond thanking him/her. Suggest some different ways that you can help him/her.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>Dear {name},</p>
                <p>Thanks for your invitation, it is very kind. I will come with pleisure!</p>
                <p>But how can I help you?</p>
                <p>I can bring some food and I also come early to install everything with you. My father have good taste for music and he can put some songs on a USB key if you want.</p>
                <p>Have a good day and I am sure your birhtday will be the best!</p>
                <p>XOXO</p>
                <p>{name}</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
